    <item>
      <title>T-Mobile 出售 5.61 亿美元无线债务交易于 8 月搁置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/t-mobile-sells-561-million-wireless-debt-deal-shelved-in-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[T-Mobile US Inc. 出售了价值逾 5 亿美元的由无线设备合同支持的债券，此前该公司在 8 月份推迟了该交易，因为当时债务市场受到一系列令人意外的经济、企业和央行消息的冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/t-mobile-sells-561-million-wireless-debt-deal-shelved-in-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 20:52:06 GMT</pubDate>
