    <item>
      <title>前 C-Quest 首席执行官 Newcombe 被指控碳信用欺诈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/former-c-quest-ceo-newcombe-charged-with-carbon-credit-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前 C-Quest Capital LLC 首席执行官肯尼斯·纽科姆 (Kenneth Newcombe) 被联邦检察官指控举报虚假的减排信息，作为获取数百万碳信用额的非法计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/former-c-quest-ceo-newcombe-charged-with-carbon-credit-fraud</guid>
