    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经典汽车运输业务因港口罢工而受到影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/car-shipping-business-vulnerable-due-to-port-strike-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[目前，东部和墨西哥湾沿岸港口罢工已进入第二天。此次罢工的连锁反应意味着，像 West Coast Shipping 这样的企业不得不将货物转至其他港口，有时成本很高。首席运营官兼联合创始人 Alex Naumov 在“彭博市场”节目中与 Scarlet Fu 谈论了罢工对他的古董车运输业务的影响以及他不得不做出的调整。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/car-shipping-business-vulnerable-due-to-port-strike-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 20:46:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>使用贝莱德代币作为抵押品越来越成为主流</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/use-of-blackrock-tokens-as-collateral-moves-closer-to-mainstream</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着一批金融公司投票通过代币化股票的使用准则，允许使用贝莱德和富兰克林邓普顿等华尔街巨头的货币市场基金代币化股票作为交易抵押品的努力取得了重大进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/use-of-blackrock-tokens-as-collateral-moves-closer-to-mainstream</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 18:55:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加息希望渺茫，日元收盘创 2022 年以来最大单日跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/yen-set-for-worst-day-since-early-2023-as-ishiba-dims-rate-hike-hopes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本新任首相石破茂表示，日本经济尚未准备好再次加息，此举震动了货币市场，导致日元遭遇两年多来最大幅度的下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/yen-set-for-worst-day-since-early-2023-as-ishiba-dims-rate-hike-hopes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 16:37:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业市场数据强劲，美联储押注受压，美国国债下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/treasuries-slide-as-resilient-job-market-data-weighs-on-fed-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国企业上个月增加的就业岗位多于预期，美国国债价格下跌，这向关注劳动力市场以寻找美联储需要大幅降息迹象的交易员发出了混合信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/treasuries-slide-as-resilient-job-market-data-weighs-on-fed-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 12:40:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东风险和美国数据影响新兴货币汇率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/emerging-stocks-jump-as-china-optimism-offsets-geopolitical-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中东冲突进一步升级的担忧影响了风险偏好，且交易员减少了对美国大幅降息的押注，新兴市场货币周三下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/emerging-stocks-jump-as-china-optimism-offsets-geopolitical-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 09:41:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：美联储第二次大幅降息承诺受阻，债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于就业数据强于预期，削弱了华尔街对美联储下次大幅降息的信心，美国国债下跌，美元上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 22:39:40 GMT</pubDate>
